<p>其中，组合权重（即所谓的权值矩阵）<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>θ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\theta</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span></span></span></span>为：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mtable rowspacing="0.25em" columnalign="right left" columnspacing="0em"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mn>11</mn></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mn>12</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mo>=</mo><mtext>softmax</mtext><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msubsup><mi>k</mi><mn>1</mn><mi>T</mi></msubsup></mrow><msqrt><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>k</mi></msub></msqrt></mfrac><mo separator="true">,</mo><mspace width="1em"/><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msubsup><mi>k</mi><mn>2</mn><mi>T</mi></msubsup></mrow><msqrt><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>k</mi></msub></msqrt></mfrac><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mn>21</mn></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mn>22</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mo>=</mo><mtext>softmax</mtext><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msubsup><mi>k</mi><mn>1</mn><mi>T</mi></msubsup></mrow><msqrt><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>k</mi></msub></msqrt></mfrac><mo separator="true">,</mo><mspace width="1em"/><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msubsup><mi>k</mi><mn>2</mn><mi>T</mi></msubsup></mrow><msqrt><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>k</mi></msub></msqrt></mfrac><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\begin{aligned}
&amp;[\theta_{11},\theta_{12}]=\text{softmax}\left(\frac{q_1k^T_1}{\sqrt{d_k}},\quad \frac{q_1k^T_2}{\sqrt{d_k}}\right)\\
&amp;[\theta_{21},\theta_{22}]=\text{softmax}\left(\frac{q_2k^T_1}{\sqrt{d_k}},\quad \frac{q_2k^T_2}{\sqrt{d_k}}\right)
\end{aligned}
